These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, april
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Birthday    | september    | april | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, sunflower
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower       | lily | sunflower | zinnia |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, january, may
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, salsa
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Birthday         | may     | january | august |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep     | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, chinchilla
1. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the cat##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Pet         | bird  | cat | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, chess, gardening
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, june
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | camping   | gardening | chess    |
| Birthday   | november | june     | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, taxi
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person driving the trike is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi | trike   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, architect, photographer
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the architect is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
2. the entrepreneur is between the owner of the turtle and the photographer##2
3. the entrepreneur is on the left of the architect##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Job   | photographer | entrepreneur | architect |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, lavender, orange
1. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes lavender and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Color    | lavender    | yellow | orange     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, grey, green
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Color   | green   | grey  | turquise  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

