.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, jet-ski
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Transport   | bus    | jet-ski      | skateboard |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

