.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, canasta
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person playing canasta is between the person playing monopoly and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Game   | monopoly | canasta | go |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, pall-mall
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
4. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | prince  | pall-mall     | montecristo |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

