There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Transport      | snowmobile | trike | bus |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

